    "description": "Give your veg a Spanish twist. Bake your rice with sweet peppers, fresh peas and smoky paprika. Then, top with charred hispi cabbage and drizzle with romesco and garlicky aioli. To finish up, you'll scatter golden almonds for crunch and you're ready to dive in. 3 or more of your 5/day.",
